author: Mark Reddie
title: 'This virus makes us stronger': Dozens of Ruby Princess crew members taken off coronavirus cruise ship
description: Almost 50 crew members are removed from the Ruby Princess to be repatriated, but hundreds remain on board, as an emotional announcement over the ship's PA system says "this virus can't break us ... it makes us stronger."
content:
Posted 
April 21, 2020 12:26:54
Almost 50 crew members from the Ruby Princess will be forced to further isolate in Sydney hotels tonight before boarding flights home over the next few days.
